1) Setup your crab environment, by executing, in order:

source /afs/cern.ch/cms/LCG/LCG-2/UI/cms_ui_env.sh
cmsenv
source /afs/cern.ch/cms/ccs/wm/scripts/Crab/crab.sh

->  Now the crab enviromnet is ready

2) edit the file crab.cfg

3) crab -create
   (you will be asked your passwd couple of times)

4) crab -submit (-c <dir name>)

